  stimulus_text = 'The following text is from a novel about a young woman who is trying to find her place in the world.  "I want to be more than just a pretty face, but I don’t know how to do that.  I feel like I’m stuck in a rut.  I’m not sure what I’m good at, or what I’m meant to be.  But I’m not going to give up.  I’m going to keep searching until I find my way."',
